# This theme is available from box-look.org and deviantart.com
# Last modified 20081127.

# Extract the archives content under ~/.pekwm/themes/ and the
# themes menu will pick it up automatically.

# Changelog:
# 2008-11-27 initial release
#  * brave, human, wine and wise themes to fit Shiki-Colors GTK Theme.

